class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">An accused sexual abuser wanted by the Lane County Sheriff’s Office on nine felony charges has been arrested by the U.S. Marshals Service in Reno, Nev., federal officials said Thursday.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">Byron Seymour Van Natta, 66, was indicted in Lane County Circuit Court in February in the sexual abuse of three female children. The abuse allegedly took place between 2000 and 2011.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"deep\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<!-- FileInclude:Normal, /csp/cms/sites/rg/assets/includes/rectangle01.csp -->\n<!-- //////////////////// Medium Rectangle 1 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ -->\n<div class=\"advert\"><div id=\"medium-rectangle-1\" data-google-query-id=\"CIfEs4HVutMCFVkrTwodIHkK7A\"><script>googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('medium-rectangle-1'); });</script><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/30582678/RGM/news/local_1__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/30582678/RGM/news/local_1\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/30582678/RGM/news/local_1\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" srcdoc=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;\"></iframe></div></div></div>\n<!-- \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ Medium Rectangle 1 //////////////////// -->\n<!--/FileInclude:Normal, /csp/cms/sites/rg/assets/includes/rectangle01.csp, took .000084 -->\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div> <!-- /.deep -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">He faces seven counts of first-­degree sexual abuse and one count each of sexual penetration with a foreign object and first-degree theft.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">The theft allegedly occurred last year. The victim was an adult, officials said.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">According to the U.S. Marshals Service, Van Natta fled Lane County as soon as he learned of the criminal investigation.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">Van Natta was “taking steps to try and avoid capture,” the Marshals Service said, and authorities learned he was likely in the Reno area. He was spotted at 2:45 p.m. Wednesday outside a Reno motel.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<p class=\"BodyText-BodyText\">He was arrested and booked into the Washoe County Jail on Wednesday and is awaiting extradition to Oregon, where he will be booked into the Lane County Jail. </p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"deep\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<!-- FileInclude:Normal, /csp/cms/sites/rg/assets/includes/rectangle02.csp -->\n<!-- //////////////////// Medium Rectangle 2 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ -->\n<div class=\"advert\"><div id=\"medium-rectangle-2\" data-google-query-id=\"CIjEs4HVutMCFVkrTwodIHkK7A\"><script>googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('medium-rectangle-2');
